comment: Gobert (UTA) makes contact with Curry's (DAL) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Barnes (DAL) makes incidental contact with Johnson (UTA) that does not affect his FOM.
Johnson (UTA) makes marginal contact with Matthews (DAL) on the screen.
Gobert (UTA) sets the screen on Matthews (DAL) without giving him room to avoid the contact.
Nowitzki (DAL) sets the screen on Ingles (UTA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Gobert (UTA) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Curry (DAL) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Matthews (DAL) makes marginal contact with Hayward (UTA) that does not affect his SQBR prior to the timeout.
Harris (DAL) reaches in and makes contact with the ball prior to Gobert's (UTA) shot attempt.
Gobert (UTA) grabs and holds Nowitzki's (DAL) arm, affecting his FOM when he attempts to retrieve the inbound.
Barnes (DAL) and Johnson (UTA) make incidental contact with one another during the loose ball.
Harris (DAL) makes marginal contact to Gobert (UTA) that does not affect his shot attempt.
Gobert (UTA) grabs and holds Nowitzki's (DAL) arm, affecting his FOM during the inbound.
After communicating with the Replay Center, it was determined that Gobert (UTA) committed the foul before Curry (DAL) released the inbound pass and an away-from-the-play foul is assessed.
Burks (UTA) makes incidental contact with Harris (DAL) that does not affect his ability to defend the play.
Barnes (DAL) makes incidental contact with Burks (UTA) that does not affect his SQBR.
The ball last touches Burks (UTA) prior to going OOB.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of UTA possession is overturned and DAL is awarded possession.
Matthews (DAL) and Hayward (UTA) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
Favors (UTA) sets the screen on Powell (DAL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of a 3pt field goal is confirmed.
Favors (UTA) sets the screen on Matthews (DAL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Diaw (UTA) and Nowitzki (DAL) briefly engage and separate following the screen.
Matthews (DAL) makes marginal contact with Ingles (UTA) that does not affect his SQBR.
Diaw (UTA) does not have part of his hand under the ball when he brings it to a pause and continues his dribble.
Barnes (DAL) does not make contact with Diaw's (UTA) arm on the shot attempt.
Ingles (UTA) and Curry (DAL) make incidental contact with one another during the loose ball.
Hayward (UTA) commits a take foul on Matthews (DAL).
Johnson (UTA) commits a take foul on Barnes (DAL).
